Population adjustment

global_economy |&gt;
  filter(Country == "Australia") |&gt;
  autoplot(GDP)








Useful in comparing populations of different size. Per capita adjustments are commonly used to compare GDP between countries.

Population adjustment

global_economy |&gt;
  filter(Country == "Australia") |&gt;
